msg: Fix issue #3207, "svn rm error message clarification for added files".

may be lost of --force is used.

before trying to repeat the desired operation.

author: hwright
msg: Stop setting the default translation domain from our JavaHL library.

(It also fixes a compilation issue in the SlikSVN JavaHL support).
